ISLAMABAD, Oct 2 (APP): A delegation of Overseas Pakistanis called on Prime Minister Imran Khan here on Friday and presented him a cheque of Rs. 10 million for Diamer Bhasha Dam.
The delegation comprised Afzal Mehmood, Sheikh Rafiq, Maroof Hussain and Majid Khan.
